    "title": "Monthly Cloud-Free Composite",
    "description": "Builds a single cloud-free RGB composite from one month of Sentinel-2 L2A imagery by selecting, per pixel, the clearest greenest acquisition (maximum B08/B03 ratio after SCL cloud masking) and applying an enhanced natural-color stretch. Adapted from a SentinelHub Custom Script by Nicolas Karasiak.",
